00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:26,080
Trương bá bá,

289
00:12:26,140 --> 00:12:27,180
cha con đâu ạ?

290
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:30,890
Tiểu Hoàn à,

291
00:12:31,540 --> 00:12:32,530
cha con

292
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:35,940
